OL,3,CFirm fined #500,000 after teen
OL,4,Capprentice loses finger
OL,6,FA company has been fined #500,000
OL,7,Fafter a teenager lost a finger in a
OL,8,Fworkplace accident.
OL,10,FThe 18-year-old apprentice was using a
OL,11,Fhorizontal bandsaw unsupervised at
OL,12,FProline Engineering Limited in
OL,13,FWorsley, Salford, on 7 November 2022.
OL,15,FOne finger was severed completely,
OL,16,Fwhile another was surgically re-
OL,17,Fattached, leaving the now 20-year-old
OL,18,Fwith very little movement and nerve
OL,19,Fdamage in the finger.
