OL,6,FThe apprentice was on a work placement
OL,7,Fand was just over a month into his
OL,8,Fstint at the firm when the incident
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,12,FSafety Executive (HSE) found he was
OL,13,Fbeing taught how to weld and after
OL,14,Fsome verbal training, the teenager was
OL,15,Fpermitted to cut lengths of steel into
OL,16,Fsections using a horizontal bandsaw,
OL,17,Fwhich was in a shipping container away
OL,18,Ffrom the main workshop.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
