OL,3,CFirm fined #500,000 after teen
OL,4,Capprentice loses finger
OL,6,FThe day the accident happened, the
OL,7,Fteenager was working unsupervised when
OL,8,Fhe noticed the bandsaw was not
OL,9,Fcompleting a full cut due to a build-
OL,10,Fup of metal debris underneath the
OL,11,Fsawblade. As he attempted to clear
OL,12,Faway the debris, his fingers came in
OL,13,Fcontact with the moving sawblade. He
OL,14,Fwas taken to hospital where he
OL,15,Fremained for six days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
