OL,3,CFirm fined #500,000 after teen
OL,4,Capprentice loses finger
OL,6,FHealth and Safety Executive inspector
OL,7,FTracy Fox said: "This young man was at
OL,8,Fthe very start of his career. As a
OL,9,Fresult of this company's failures, he
OL,10,Fsustained serious and irreversible
OL,11,Finjuries that have been truly life
OL,12,Fchanging.
OL,14,F"Those injuries have impacted on many
OL,15,Faspects of his life and resulted in
OL,16,Fhim having to undergo numerous
OL,17,Foperations and procedures. Once a keen
OL,18,Fmountain biker and member of his local
OL,19,Fgym, his hand grip is such that he can
OL,20,Fno longer take part in those
OL,21,Factivities that he used to love."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
