OL,3,CFirm fined #500,000 after teen
OL,4,Capprentice loses finger
OL,6,FThe investigation found Proline
OL,7,FEngineering Limited failed to carry
OL,8,Fout a suitable and sufficient risk
OL,9,Fassessment and had failed to put in
OL,10,Fplace an adequate safe system of work.
OL,12,FIt also revealed inconsistencies and
OL,13,Finadequacies in the provision of
OL,14,Finformation, instruction, training and
OL,15,Fsupervision for those required to use
OL,16,Fthe bandsaw.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
