OL,3,CFirm fined #500,000 after teen
OL,4,Capprentice loses finger
OL,6,FThe company pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fbreaching Section 2(1) of the Health
OL,8,Fand Safety at Work etc Act 1974 at
OL,9,FManchester Magistrates' Court. It was
OL,10,Ffined #500,000 and ordered to pay
OL,11,F#5,317 costs.
OL,13,FMs Fox added: "Had even the most basic
OL,14,Fsafeguards been put in place this
OL,15,Fincident would have been avoided. The
OL,16,Frisks arising from operating machines
OL,17,Fsuch as bandsaws are well known. HSE
OL,18,Fhas clear guidance on the provision
OL,19,Fand used of work equipment that can
OL,20,Fhelp in preventing incidents like this
OL,21,Ffrom happening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
