OL,6,F"We would like highlight that all
OL,7,Femployers should make sure they
OL,8,Fproperly assess their workplace for
OL,9,Fthese risks and act to ensure that
OL,10,Feffective measures are in place to
OL,11,Fminimise the risks associated with
OL,12,Foperating machinery.
OL,14,F"It is crucial that as part of this
OL,15,Fassessment employers consider and
OL,16,Fmanage any increased risks that may be
OL,17,Fassociated with inexperienced
OL,18,Femployees."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
